{"tid":1857774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要說我支持醫護罷工 試着說我會同醫護一齊罷工","createTime":"2020-02-02T10:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T11:59:58.000Z","uid":187796,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1274b7ee1e14d97139a5578b17654900ca1adfc0","tid":1857774,"uid":187796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:31:03.000Z","msg":"一齊罷，唔係醫護自己罷。<br />\n一齊罷，唔係醫護自己罷。<br />\n一齊罷，唔係醫護自己罷。<br />\n<br />\n今次好有可能係最有威力嘅一次罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就算醫護手足係主力但佢地<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔係condom</span></span>，我地講過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">齊上齊落</span>唔只係口號。<br />\n<br />\n2月3，一齊罷。<br />\n不封關，不上班。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eq2MjxL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Feq2MjxL.jpg&h=2ce02e38&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TgV91L5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTgV91L5.jpg&h=ea42e221&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x63ztq6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx63ztq6.jpg&h=0ff66d54&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nWYDaEs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnWYDaEs.jpg&h=29bdeadd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92e63f649a5cca530d909988423760c6f383f9f4","tid":1857774,"uid":187796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:31:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb9451b63e681ecdef6aa9ef522aff64413c251f","tid":1857774,"uid":295548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:31:25.000Z","msg":"《天滅中共賦》<br />\n<br />\n共黨臣民 作惡多端<br />\n外侵諸邦 內屠義士<br />\n赤匪所至 寸草不生<br />\n禍國殃民 血債累累<br />\n習妖維尼 逆天而行<br />\n自立為帝 天怒人怨<br />\n庚子伊始 天譴將臨<br />\n大仙報夢 國運已盡<br />\n共黨治下 必有七患<br />\n正月武肺 播毒中原<br />\n二月流感 飛禽盡亡<br />\n三月地震 血流成河<br />\n四月豬瘟 百物騰升<br />\n五月飢荒 易子而食<br />\n六月內戰 析骸而爨<br />\n七月水災 長江決堤<br />\n炎共將亡 水德當立<br />\n歲在庚子 